@DATABASE "Beyond The Ice Palace"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Beyond The Ice Palace"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                           Beyond The Ice Palace
                           =====================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37424,255)"}          37424,x (x = 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I removed the "No Enemies" POKE because it didn't
                         work - it removed your weapons instead! I also
                         removed the "Immunity" POKE as well, because it
                         did sod all.

                         Rastan.
@endnode
